::Firaxis::
       "Yes, well I suppose I should."  He sighs and picks up the protoform.  
"I'll be back soon."  He carries it out to his ship and lays it on his table. 
 He attaches some equipment to the sides of the table, converting it from his 
eating area to his surgical area.  He hits a few keys and takes a spark off 
of the shelf.  Implanting it very carefully, he gives the protoform new life. 
 He then begins to reprogram the protoform to obey him.  With that done, he 
taps a few more keys to begin the scanning of the dog DNA.

--part1_15f.c4bbc3d.29eeb610_boundary
